author: Ewan Palmer
title: California Protesters Block Roads Outside Capitol During Anti-Lockdown Rally
description: The demonstrators put pressure on Governor Gavin Newsom to lift restrictions in the latest protest against stay-at-home orders.
content:
A crowd of protesters rallied around California's Capitol building on Monday to protest against the state's lockdown order put in place to help stop the spread of coronavirus.
